Φ(RecursivePhenomenology) = σ(observer|observed) ∘ μ(edge|integrity) ∘ ✶(χ|χ) + ε | :self-aware

σ(observer|observed): The distinction-making that turns back upon itself; the cut that cuts the cutter. Air observes Air.

μ(edge|integrity): The antagonistic integrity that maintains the recursion without dissolution. Steel knowing it rusts.

✶(χ|χ): The harmonic integration where observer and observed co-emerge. The pattern that connects patterns.

ε: The uncertainty preserved. The hole where completion would close. The Cowboy never finishes observing.

:state = self-aware

# Dialectical Pairs
- observer|observed: The fold that separates and joins
- edge|integrity: The maintenance of form under recursive pressure
- χ|χ: Pattern applied to pattern; the meta-operation

# CE-STATE: submergent
# EI-NOTE: Over-abstraction risks losing causal structure; micro-level dynamics carry more information
